Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.80,0:00:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you just admit that\Nyou're freaked out by my robot hand?\N{\rDefault_1}你為什麼不肯承認你被我的機械手臂嚇壞了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.50,0:00:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not freaked out by- it's...\N{\rDefault_1}我沒有害怕， 只是...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.00,0:00:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...alright! Fine!\N{\rDefault_1}... 好好好！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.00,0:00:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm freaked out! I have nightmares\Nthat I'm being chased...\N{\rDefault_1}我承認 我被嚇傻了！ 我還做惡夢被它追著跑...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.00,0:00:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...by these giant robotic claws of death...\N{\rDefault_1}... 被這些巨大的奪命機器爪子追殺...
