Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.00,0:00:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Robot's memory synced and locked!\N{\rDefault_1}機器人記憶同步鎖定完成！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.00,0:01:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This is pretty freaky.\N{\rDefault_1}這個挺詭異的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.00,0:01:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't you be down there?\N{\rDefault_1}你是不是該下去了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.00,0:02:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you guys talking last night.\N{\rDefault_1}我昨天聽到你們這些傢伙的談話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.00,0:02:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not my fault, you know.\N{\rDefault_1}你知道的， 這不是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.00,0:03:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you ready?\N{\rDefault_1}準備好了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.00,0:03:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course you're ready, you're a rockstar.\N{\rDefault_1}你當然準備好了， 你是個搖滾明星嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.00,0:03:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How's it looking, Barley?\N{\rDefault_1}情況如何， 貝里？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.00,0:03:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We should have about ten minutes...\N{\rDefault_1}我們應該有10分鐘左右的時間...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.50,0:03:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well that's perfect.\N{\rDefault_1}好的， 棒極了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.50,0:03:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We're on in one! All systems go!\NYeah you, go!\N{\rDefault_1}一分鐘後開始！ 全部的系統啟動！\N對， 你也是， 快點！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.00,0:03:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Go! Move your asses! Go go go!\N{\rDefault_1}快！ 動起來！ 快快快！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.00,0:03:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I love it! Come on, go!\N{\rDefault_1}這個我喜歡！ 拜託， 快！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.00,0:03:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's nice.\N{\rDefault_1}很好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.50,0:03:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing to worry about.\N{\rDefault_1}沒什麼好擔心的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.00,0:03:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thom.\N{\rDefault_1}湯姆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.00,0:03:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There she is.\N{\rDefault_1}她在那
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.50,0:03:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Now.\N{\rDefault_1}就是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:03:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You love her.\N{\rDefault_1}你是愛她的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.00,0:03:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,She is your passion!\N{\rDefault_1}她就是你的熱情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.00,0:04:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Be tender to her.\N{\rDefault_1}溫柔點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.50,0:04:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Be honest! Eh- be tender.\N{\rDefault_1}要誠懇！ 溫柔些
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.00,0:04:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Remind her what love is.\N{\rDefault_1}讓她回憶起什麼是愛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.00,0:04:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...and, action!\N{\rDefault_1}... 好， 開演！
