Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.00,0:05:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Look Celia.\N{\rDefault_1}聽著， 希莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.00,0:05:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to follow our passions.\N{\rDefault_1}我們必須順著我們的感覺走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You have your robotics...\N{\rDefault_1}你熱愛機械工學...
